{"tid":2216790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[XX 航空] 買完機票竟然冇得搭飛機？","createTime":"2020-09-25T03:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T08:44:39.000Z","uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf088dd59dba2f2fa4e68d75fc527ab3be5ac22","tid":2216790,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:27:51.000Z","msg":"大家起起我底，<br />\n都知我平時最撐XX航空架啦，<br />\n所以今次中秋節，要買機票比女朋友去東京玩，<br />\n我都特登揀XX。<br />\n<br />\n點知今日去到counter check-in 時，<br />\n佢先同我講全線冇晒東京，<br />\n仲想叫我不如去北京算啦。<br />\n<br />\n打電話去 CS 投訴，<br />\n佢話一係退錢一係去北京，<br />\n仲用張機票條款大我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0936bf273723fb65290a415fcab84a1afa07bef4","tid":2216790,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"根本日本都唔會畀你入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def6d0f36f0809ab75ae90a61d0db8b35eda8fec","tid":2216790,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:33:18.000Z","msg":"做生意講信用，最緊要就係老實，<br />\n你賣得東京機票就要預客人去東京，而唔係去北京。<br />\n我就係睇中你東京機票有特價、時間又靚，先幫襯你。<br />\n冇晒位又唔通知人（我係上網訂，有記錄架喎）<br />\n<br />\n我訂個時又唔見你個網有寫條款？<br />\n條款夠寫唔可以換錢，佢又唔跟？<br />\n<br />\n而家來到 counter 先發現冇得 check-in，我都唔知邊到嘔個東京機票黎比女朋友<br />\n一早比晒錢訂野真係把撚，一句冇位就比想打發人<br />\n<br />\nXX，你係咪應該乞又好、自己整又好，<br />\n嘔返一張東京 ticket 比我，事後你既額外支出，<br />\n係自己搞掂佢，而唔係搵支持者硬食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d85f353811a8aaf9f38ab2dffe4bb95a879d7f","tid":2216790,"uid":200070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:39:17.000Z","msg":"XX係乜春"},{"pid":"592eaef9ed0a48bef1fef0b01c6079a93046fbc3","tid":2216790,"uid":18381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:39:33.000Z","msg":"開名啦"},{"pid":"f46839214c1b049de6bfa02108c231efeb281b13","tid":2216790,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:40:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d023de63503e822a9c4f96fc65a5a095e8762ba","tid":2216790,"uid":375425,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:51:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f69aaa2ae3e49825d903ac79a1e60accc5de1de","tid":2216790,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T08:44:39.000Z","msg":"龍門月餅？"}]}